Overview of making a new application using ng cli:

ng new biot-interface
    - creates a blank new application

cd biot-interface    

ng g directive threed
    - creates a blank new directive called threed

ng g service threed.service/threed
    - creates a blank new service (threed.service) in its own directory

ng g component about/about
    - creates a blank new component (about) in its own directory

ng g component nodes/nodes
    - creates another blank new component (nodes) in its own directory

etc etc...

CHROME_BIN=`which chromium-browser` ng test
    - tests the app

